{"type": "article", "id": 24601, "title": "HAY和COS联手推出春季系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-29T06:59:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607174259BMN95xDp6nH3WE1s.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">丹麦品牌 HAY 和时尚品牌 COS 有多次合作和联合门店，这是他们新推出的 2016 春季家居系列。将一些 HAY 原有的配件设计放在绿、蓝、粉这三种更加活泼明快的颜色中，可以组成系列。COS 的设计师 Martin Andersson 称“我们想要让 HAY 的东西有 COS 的感觉”。这些产品目前可以在 COS 的门店和网站上找到，<a href=\"http://www.cosstores.com/gb/COSxHAY/All\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174257fqPiXCOEjyUth0nS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174258SL8AvI6k7Keyiz3H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174258KCf4vPmTMWJyA2Zw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174259Ten5EmUjOQ8vSgwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}